snippet.title: Evan Rachel Wood Talks About Her Fight For Domestic Abuse Victims | TODAY
snippet.description:
Evan Rachel Wood talks to NBC’s Maria Shriver about advocating for domestic violence survivors and her personal connection to the cause. In April, Wood testified about her past trauma to the California Senate in an effort to push a new bill, the Phoenix Act.
